column5: Any?  While I was being bored to death at a wedding I kept thinking of you lucky guys fishing.
If you are talking about the big OFC G2G, that's not until November 15-16....so you didn't miss anything yet!  There are a few BOQ reports from some members floating around the board though.
... and it's still early enough to make plans to attend so you can write your own report!!!  Wear warm clothes if you go... make sure you have fresh batteries for the camera too!!!
